review_text: Pretty little green area before you get into plaza days are Metro a little respite from your running around downtown

(Translated by Google) This small neighborhood park has really been remodeling a lot lately.Much more friendly and welcoming.Hello to the designer of this project that has highlighted the titled sculpture "The celestial tramps" which is a tribute to all forms of mutual assistance to improve the living conditions of homeless people.

(Original)
Ce petit parc de quartier s"est véritablement fait refaire toute une beauté dernièrement.  Beaucoup plus convivial et accueillant.  Bravo au concepteur de ce projet qui a su mettre en valeur la sculpture titrée "Les clochards célestes" qui se veut un hommage à toutes les formes d’entraide en vue d’améliorer les conditions de vie des personnes itinérantes.

(Translated by Google) A small street corner park. OK to wait for the bus in the summer but that's it.
